---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Slide from '@components/Slide.astro';
---

<Layout>

  <!-- ── Intro ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="intro" colorBg="grey-light" colorInner="primary" triggerAlwaysVisible>
    <div class="heading">
      <h1 class="title h2">Alker</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Clarity is where momentum begins. When direction is clear, action
        follows. That's when good ideas finally move forward.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        Alker is the strategic advisory practice of Jürgen Alker, built on
        30 years of experience turning ideas, brands, and ventures into
        commercial impact.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Intro 2 ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="intro-1" colorBg="grey-light" colorInner="primary">
    <div class="heading">
      <!-- no pretitle on this slide -->
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        He works closely with entrepreneurs, investors, and decision-makers.
        Together, they navigate complexity with clarity, shape smart
        strategies, and stay close to execution. No noise. No layers.
        Nothing unnecessary.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p class="tagline">Less noise.<br />More momentum.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── About (portrait) ──────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide
    id="about"
    colorBg="primary"
    colorInner="grey-light"
    triggerInverted
    imageMobile="/images/portrait-mobile.webp"
    imageDesktop="/images/portrait-desktop.webp"
    imageAlt="portrait of Jürgen Alker"
  >
    <div class="heading">
      <h2 class="title h2">About</h2>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── About 2 (text) ───────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="about-1" colorBg="grey-light" colorInner="grey-dark">
    <div class="heading">
      <h2 class="title h2">About</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content is-small">
      <p>
        Jürgen Alker has spent over three decades turning ideas into
        tangible outcomes. He has helped launch global brands, scale
        businesses, and build ventures from the ground up. He also founded
        his own agency and took it from idea to exit.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        Today, he partners with a select group of entrepreneurs, investors,
        and decision-makers to navigate complexity with clarity, move
        faster, and execute with confidence.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        His approach is hands-on, independent, and rooted in trust over
        templates. The goal is always the same: turning direction into
        action and delivering commercial impact.
      </p>
      <br />
      →&nbsp;<a
        href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1gLtWk3iY2iHrXB-QxBMHyrfswl7xUhnWgBHzWBQYAoo/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.li83jhu7zufk"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="external link to full CV"
      >
        Full CV
      </a>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principles intro ──────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <h2 class="title h2">Principles</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>These are the principles that guide the way Alker works.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 1 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-1" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Trust is non-negotiable</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Everything meaningful starts with mutual trust. Transparency and reliability go both ways.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 2 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-2" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Clarity over complexity</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Complicated plans get ignored. Clear strategies drive action.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 3 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-3" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Direct conversations only</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>No middlemen. No layers. Work happens directly with people who can move.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 4 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-4" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Execution is what matters</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Ideas are everywhere. Turning them into results is what makes the difference.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 5 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-5" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Impact beats activity</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Incremental steps are fine. But the goal is meaningful progress, not busywork.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 6 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-6" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">No ego. No hierarchy</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Titles don't matter. What counts is what moves things forward.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 7 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-7" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Forget the drama</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>What matters is what gets done.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Principle 8 ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="principles-8" colorBg="grey-dark" colorInner="grey-light">
    <div class="heading">
      <span class="pretitle">Principles</span>
      <h2 class="title h2">Let's make sure to have fun along the way</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>The best work happens when we're enjoying ourselves.</p>
    </div>
  </Slide>

  <!-- ── Contact ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <Slide id="contact" colorBg="light" colorInner="dark" triggerAlwaysVisible>
    <div class="heading">
      <h2 class="title h2">Contact</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content flex">
      <div class="contact">
        <div class="column">
          <p class="cta">
            How to reach me:
            <a href="mailto:j@alker.io" aria-label="mailto link to j@alker.io">
              j@alker.io
            </a>
          </p>
          <p class="cta">
            Subscribe to my
            <a
              href="https://alker.substack.com/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              aria-label="external link to newsletter"
            >
              newsletter
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="column socials">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/juergenalker/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            title="LinkedIn"
            aria-label="LinkedIn profile"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M35.1667 0.5C36.3159 0.5 37.4181 0.956546 38.2308 1.7692C39.0435 2.58186 39.5 3.68406 39.5 4.83333V35.1667C39.5 36.3159 39.0435 37.4181 38.2308 38.2308C37.4181 39.0435 36.3159 39.5 35.1667 39.5H4.83333C3.68406 39.5 2.58186 39.0435 1.7692 38.2308C0.956546 37.4181 0.5 36.3159 0.5 35.1667V4.83333C0.5 3.68406 0.956546 2.58186 1.7692 1.7692C2.58186 0.956546 3.68406 0.5 4.83333 0.5H35.1667ZM34.0833 34.0833V22.6C34.0833 20.7267 33.3392 18.9301 32.0145 17.6055C30.6899 16.2808 28.8933 15.5367 27.02 15.5367C25.1783 15.5367 23.0333 16.6633 21.9933 18.3533V15.9483H15.9483V34.0833H21.9933V23.4017C21.9933 21.7333 23.3367 20.3683 25.005 20.3683C25.8095 20.3683 26.581 20.6879 27.1499 21.2568C27.7188 21.8256 28.0383 22.5972 28.0383 23.4017V34.0833H34.0833ZM8.90667 12.5467C9.87206 12.5467 10.7979 12.1632 11.4805 11.4805C12.1632 10.7979 12.5467 9.87206 12.5467 8.90667C12.5467 6.89167 10.9217 5.245 8.90667 5.245C7.93553 5.245 7.00417 5.63078 6.31748 6.31748C5.63078 7.00417 5.245 7.93553 5.245 8.90667C5.245 10.9217 6.89167 12.5467 8.90667 12.5467ZM11.9183 34.0833V15.9483H5.91667V34.0833H11.9183Z" fill="currentColor" />
            </svg>
          </a>

          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/alker/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            title="Instagram"
            aria-label="Instagram profile"
          >
            <svg viewBox="0 0 44 44" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M12.8987 0.333008H31.0987C38.032 0.333008 43.6654 5.96634 43.6654 12.8997V31.0997C43.6654 34.4326 42.3414 37.6289 39.9847 39.9856C37.628 42.3424 34.4316 43.6663 31.0987 43.6663H12.8987C5.96536 43.6663 0.332031 38.033 0.332031 31.0997V12.8997C0.332031 9.56679 1.65602 6.37041 4.01272 4.0137C6.36943 1.65699 9.56581 0.333008 12.8987 0.333008ZM12.4654 4.66634C10.3699 4.66634 8.36022 5.4989 6.88494 6.97418C5.40965 8.44946 4.57703 10.4591 4.57703 12.5547V31.4447C4.57703 35.813 8.09703 39.333 12.4654 39.333H31.5354C33.6309 39.333 35.6405 38.5004 37.1158 37.0251C38.5911 35.5499 39.4237 33.5402 39.4237 31.4447V12.5547C39.4237 8.18634 35.9037 4.66634 31.5354 4.66634H12.4654ZM33.3987 7.83301C34.0837 7.83301 34.7407 8.10556 35.2252 8.59003C35.7097 9.0745 35.9822 9.73138 35.9822 10.4163C35.9822 11.1013 35.7097 11.7582 35.2252 12.2427C34.7407 12.7271 34.0837 12.9997 33.3987 12.9997C32.7137 12.9997 32.0568 12.7271 31.5723 12.2427C31.0878 11.7582 30.8154 11.1013 30.8154 10.4163C30.8154 9.73138 31.0878 9.0745 31.5723 8.59003C32.0568 8.10556 32.7137 7.83301 33.3987 7.83301ZM21.9987 10.9997C24.8292 10.9997 27.5441 12.1238 29.5445 14.1242C31.5449 16.1246 32.6654 18.8395 32.6654 21.6663C32.6654 24.4932 31.5449 27.2081 29.5445 29.2085C27.5441 31.2089 24.8292 32.333 21.9987 32.333C19.1719 32.333 16.457 31.2089 14.4566 29.2085C12.4562 27.2081 11.332 24.4932 11.332 21.6663C11.332 18.8395 12.4562 16.1246 14.4566 14.1242C16.457 12.1238 19.1719 10.9997 21.9987 10.9997ZM21.9987 15.333C20.3411 15.333 18.7514 15.9926 17.5762 17.1678C16.401 18.343 15.7654 19.9327 15.7654 21.5903C15.7654 23.248 16.401 24.8377 17.5762 26.0129C18.7514 27.1881 20.3411 27.8477 21.9987 27.8477C23.6563 27.8477 25.246 27.1881 26.4212 26.0129C27.5964 24.8377 28.232 23.248 28.232 21.5903C28.232 19.9327 27.5964 18.343 26.4212 17.1678C25.246 15.9926 23.6563 15.333 21.9987 15.333Z" fill="currentColor" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Slide>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* ── Slide content layout ─────────────────────────── */
  .heading {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.875rem;
  }

  .pretitle {
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
  }

  /* content block inside slides */
  .content {
    max-width: 78.125rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .content.is-small {
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
  }

  .content.flex {
    max-width: none;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-weight: var(--fw-black);
    font-size: var(--fs-2);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* ── Contact layout ───────────────────────────────── */
  .contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3.125rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .contact {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }
  }

  .cta {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 12ch;
    font-size: clamp(
      2rem,
      2200 / (var(--fluid-max) - var(--fluid-min)) * 1vw +
        (var(--fluid-min) * 54 - var(--fluid-max) * 32) /
        (var(--fluid-min) - var(--fluid-max)) / 16 * 1rem,
      3.375rem
    );
  }

  @media (min-width: 560px) {
    .cta {
      max-width: none;
    }
  }

  .socials {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .socials a {
    width: clamp(
      2rem,
      800 / (var(--fluid-max) - var(--fluid-min)) * 1vw +
        (var(--fluid-min) * 40 - var(--fluid-max) * 32) /
        (var(--fluid-min) - var(--fluid-max)) / 16 * 1rem,
      2.5rem
    );
    height: clamp(
      2rem,
      800 / (var(--fluid-max) - var(--fluid-min)) * 1vw +
        (var(--fluid-min) * 40 - var(--fluid-max) * 32) /
        (var(--fluid-min) - var(--fluid-max)) / 16 * 1rem,
      2.5rem
    );
  }

  .socials a svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
